HUMBOLDT MISCHIEF.

37:15.680 --> 37:18.399
- DO NOT LIGHT THAT.
DO NOT--

37:18.440 --> 37:20.021
- CROSBY, IF YOU GET ME
KICKED OUT OF THIS SCHOOL,

37:20.060 --> 37:22.233
